Cobb who is played by 
Leonardo DiCaprio is a thief with the rare ability to enter people's dreams and steal their secrets from their subconscious.  Cobb (dicaprio) is offered a seemingly impossible task: Plant an idea in someone's mind. If he succeeds, it will be the perfect crime.
I would say its worth watching. Even if you don't understand the premise of the movie it is still great to watch the all star cast of actors in the movie.
Wow ok that sounds like something I would watch Im surprised that I have not seen it
